title: Madden NFL 16 Roster Update For Week 6 of the NFL Season Available Now
text: Madden NFL 16 Roster Update For Week 6 of the NFL Season Available Now 04:47 PM - October 15, 2015 by Steve_OS Week 6 of the NFL season is here and so are the updated Madden NFL 16 rosters. Check out the blog here , along with the sortable spreadsheet of all changes here. GOING UP Odell Beckham Jr. +1 (94) Andy Dalton +2 (87) # 1 Blazerfan07 @ 10/15/15 05:03 PM Is the sortable spreadsheet blank for anyone else? # 2 strife1013 @ 10/15/15 09:39 PM No issue with spread sheet for me. Does anyone know if they ever change a players development trait progression with roster updates since it's not editable for us even in main menu where you are able to edit everything for a player. # 3 garyraymond23 @ 10/16/15 06:54 AM Happy to see Freeman continue to rise, however I don't understand why Julio is now having is rating going down when it's blatantly obvious he's had a consistent hamstring injury for weeks?
